          <num>12-504d</num>
          <heading>Appeals</heading>
          <content>
            <p>Sec. 12-504d. Appeals.Any person aggrieved by the imposition of a tax under the provisions of sections 12504a to 12504f, inclusive, may appeal therefrom as provided in sections12-111,12-112and12-118. If the time for appealing to the board of assessment appeals has passed, the taxpayer may appeal at the next regularly scheduled meeting.
